data.description:
VA Assumable loan @ 2.25% also available! Luxurious Ranch-Style Home in The Canyons of Castle Pines. Your dream home in one of South Denver's most prestigious neighborhoods! This stunning property offers an array of impressive features:
5 bedrooms and 4 bathrooms, provides ample space for your family's needs. Enjoy the convenience and extra storage space provided by the three-car garage. An Award-Winning Community, the Canyons of Castle Pines was awarded "2022 Community Of The Year" by the Home Builders Association of Metro Denver. The gourmet chef's kitchen is a culinary delight, featuring high-end luxury appliances including a Viking Stove with 6 burners and grille, Quartz countertops, an oversized kitchen island, custom stacked upper cabinets, and built-in pantry organization. The main living area connects seamlessly to an outdoor covered patio through overlapping sliding glass doors featuring an outdoor natural gas, built in firepit and low maintenance turf grass. The main floor master retreat offers an En suite master bath with a free-standing tub, frameless glass shower, dual vanities, and access to a custom walk-in closet.
The finished walk out basement boasts 10 ft ceilings, 3 bedrooms, and 1 full bath, providing additional living space. Enjoy community amenities including The Exchange coffee house, a resort-style pool, and the upcoming Canyon House, featuring a residents-only bar/restaurant, fitness center, meeting rooms, and a covered terrace. Sellers have invested over $150K in post-purchase options, making this home truly exceptional. This home includes central A/C, a 90% high-efficiency furnace, and a tankless water heater, as well as a Smart Home System and three Eero Networking routers to boost signal. Don't miss the opportunity to own this exquisite home with unparalleled features and community amenities.
